OL,3,CConcerns over 'ridiculous' payout for
OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,FThey were offered a one-off #15,000
OL,7,Fpayment on top of the ongoing support,
OL,8,Fwith a #10,000 award available for
OL,9,Fothers in similar, less notorious
OL,10,Fcases.
OL,12,FChanges to the payment are currently
OL,13,Fsubject to public consultation.
OL,15,FThe Hepatitis C Trust has written to
OL,16,FCabinet Office minister Nick Thomas-
OL,17,FSymonds to "express our profound
OL,18,Fconcerns regarding the proposed
OL,19,Fcompensation for victims of unethical
OL,20,Fresearch within the infected blood
OL,21,Fcompensation scheme".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
