OL,3,CConcerns over 'ridiculous' payout for
OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,FThe charity said that the sums are
OL,7,F"wholly inadequate".
OL,9,F"We are very concerned that the
OL,10,Fcurrent proposals fall far short of
OL,11,Fdelivering justice and risk sending a
OL,12,Fdangerous message about the value of
OL,13,Fhuman life and the integrity of public
OL,14,Finstitutions in the UK," the letter
OL,15,Fadds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
