OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1768677310
OL,3,CConcerns over 'ridiculous' payout for
OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,F"You are more than aware of the
OL,7,Fimmense suffering of the victims of
OL,8,Fwhat has been termed 'unethical
OL,9,Fresearch' - people, most of whom were
OL,10,Fchildren, who were deliberately given
OL,11,Fblood products known to be
OL,12,Fcontaminated with HIV, hepatitis B,
OL,13,Fand hepatitis C.
OL,15,F"This was not an accident; it was a
OL,16,Fconscious decision by medical
OL,17,Fprofessionals."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
