OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,FSignatories, including the charity,
OL,7,Fand other members of the infected
OL,8,Fblood community, called for the award
OL,9,Fto be "fully and transparently
OL,10,Freviewed".
OL,12,FGary Webster, who was infected with
OL,13,FHIV and hepatitis C when he attend
OL,14,FTreloar's in the 1970s and 80s, told
OL,15,Fthe Press Association that a revised
OL,16,Fpotential offer of #25,000 was still
OL,17,F"way off the mark".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
