OL,3,CConcerns over 'ridiculous' payout for
OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,FHe added: "How can you offer #25,000
OL,7,Fpounds to someone who's been
OL,8,Fexperimented and researched on, and
OL,9,Fmost of the time killed?
OL,11,F"It's just ridiculous. It has to be a
OL,12,Flot more than what they are offering."
OL,14,F"He said of the 122 haemophiliac boys
OL,15,Fwho attended the college, more than 80
OL,16,Fare now dead."
OL,18,F"We were forced, basically to have
OL,19,Finjections every day," Mr Webster said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
