OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1768677310
OL,3,CConcerns over 'ridiculous' payout for
OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,F"At the time, we didn't know - we were
OL,7,Feight, nine, 10, years old - and we
OL,8,Fjust thought the doctors, who were our
OL,9,Ffriends, who used to come and play
OL,10,Fsports with us in the evening, we
OL,11,Fthought they were doing good for us.
OL,13,F"Our parents had no knowledge of
OL,14,Fanything.
OL,16,F"All haemophiliacs throughout the UK
OL,17,Fwere researched and experimented on
OL,18,Fone way or another, but especially at
OL,19,FTreloar's it was constant."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
