OL,3,CConcerns over 'ridiculous' payout for
OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,FElsewhere, the letter also raises
OL,7,Fconcerns over delays to potential
OL,8,Fcriminal investigation into the
OL,9,Fscandal.
OL,11,FAfter the inquiry published its
OL,12,Ffindings in May 2024, the National
OL,13,FPolice Chiefs' Council (NPCC)
OL,14,Finstigated a review to determine
OL,15,Fwhether a national criminal
OL,16,Finvestigation could or should follow.
OL,18,FIn December, it said that the review
OL,19,Fis "ongoing".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
