OL,3,CConcerns over 'ridiculous' payout for
OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,FThe new letter states: "They (the
OL,7,FNPCC) give no timeline for completion.
OL,8,FThis delay compounds the injustice and
OL,9,Ferodes public trust."
OL,11,FSignatories of the letter called for a
OL,12,F"clear timeline or decisions on
OL,13,Fcriminal accountability".
OL,15,FA Government spokesperson said: "The
OL,16,Fsuffering endured by all those
OL,17,Fsubjected to unethical medical
OL,18,Fresearch is profound, and we remain
OL,19,Fcommitted to ensuring that justice is
OL,20,Fnot only delivered but reflected in
OL,21,Fthe way compensation is treated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
