OL,3,CConcerns over 'ridiculous' payout for
OL,4,CHampshire infected blood victims
OL,6,F"This is why uplifts to the Autonomy
OL,7,Fawards will be made available through
OL,8,Fthe supplementary route to recognise
OL,9,Fthe suffering of victims subjected to
OL,10,Funethical research practices.
OL,12,F"This award is just one part of the
OL,13,Foverall compensation package available.
OL,15,F"We encourage the community to respond
OL,16,Fto the government's consultation
OL,17,Fbefore 22 January, which seeks
OL,18,Frespondents' feedback on different
OL,19,Fways of designing and calculating the
OL,20,Faward to reflect unethical research
OL,21,Fpractices."
